§0
§4§oThere is no entrance §4§ofee for LSIF, we will§0
§4§onever ask anything§0
§4§oof you except a §0
§4§oritualistic labor of§0
§4§ocharcoal-production§0
§4§oduring initiation.§0
§0
§0
§4§lSo please join us§0
§4§l      today!
